<p>Mini-Heap posts usually appear when 7 or so new items accumulate in the <a class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="https://dailynous.com/heap-of-links/">Heap of Links</a>, a collection of items from around the web that may be of interest to philosophers. The Heap of Links consists partly of suggestions from readers; if you find something online that you think would be of interest to the philosophical community, please <a class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="mailto:dailynouseditor@gmail.com">send it in</a> for consideration for the Heap. Thank you.<br class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image" /><em class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><a class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="https://dailynous.com/2025/03/20/mini-heap-644/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Previous Edition</a> </em></p><p>The post <a href="https://dailynous.com/2025/03/26/mini-heap-645/">Mini-Heap</a> first appeared on <a href="https://dailynous.com">Daily Nous</a>.</p>